wiki_section_text: 24 candidates competed for the title .

intro: Miss Venezuela 2011 was the 58th edition of the Miss Venezuela pageant held on October 15, 2011 at the Estudio 1 de Venevisión in Caracas, Venezuela. At the end of the event, outgoing titleholder Vanessa Gonçalves crowned Irene Esser of Sucre as her successor.
